questions.quote: OK, we done with the chit-chat? Are we ready to play some serious poker?
Alright, I can't, I can't wait that long. You have to do something-knock that door down!
Well, the end table is wrong, The couch looks bizarre and don't even get me started on the refrigerator magnets.
Okay, okay, okay. Y'know what, this was just really expensive. And I'll take- this was a gift.
Stop talking, stop talking now. Let me just get this straight. You're actually stealing my hat?
Right, I mean, come on, I'm sure that if you had a funeral or a memorial service, tons of people would come.
Wh-What are you talking about? It wasn't a girl. It was this huge dude.
Groomsman, groomsman, why are you just standing there, where is your bridesmaid? We've got a broken arrow. Bridesmaid down! Oh, that's me.
Look at you! What-You're-you're this big executive! You are much more capable than you give yourself credit for. I-I have no doubt you're gonna be an incredible mother.
Ohh. Um-hmm. But y'know, she choose to find me. I mean, I have to respect her decision. Right?
